## 🛡️ Why Choose MedCore?
1.  **Private Cloud:** Most companies sell "SaaS" where your data is mixed with thousands of others. We give you a **Private Instance** for maximum security.
2.  **Zero Dependency:** You own your data. You can export your entire clinic ledger in 1-click in CSV/Excel format at any time.
3.  **Physiotherapy Optimized:** The clinical markers and vitals are specifically configured for your workflow, unlike generic hospital software.

